This plugin was an idea I got after re-watching the yogcast. In episode 10 when simon 
walked out the backdoor and the boobytrap went off, I thought, what if you could do that 
to people without pressure plates? That way they could never see it coming and it would 
be an even bigger surprise. Currently a WIP.

Do not copy or alter without my permission, you can contact me at jacob_perry@hotmail.ca if you have any questions.